{"tid":2510891,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"點解1000mb 上網電腦出得100mb？","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T17:58:15.000Z","uid":58069,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c45551472c02777a4b2e772bff6a6a0bacc684dd","tid":2510891,"uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"我modem用cat6線駁router出到800mb WiFi<br />\n同一個modem port位同一條線駁電腦得番100mb<br />\n係咪底板port位收左皮？<br />\n底板係b450m-pro gaming. <br />\n網卡setting set 到 1gbs full duplex.<br />\n乙太網絡出果個速度得100mb<br />\n底板壞左 買WiFi 手指打機有冇問題？<br />\n求救<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d4d0b0bc73aca23bb4eca798718bd270d61a6c","tid":2510891,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7aa5c63ac807abd5423a969cb88f765f8ae327","tid":2510891,"uid":168384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:12:45.000Z","msg":"56k已足夠"},{"pid":"4014c8eb090fdbe68b0f9d1d400db6e1e824254d","tid":2510891,"uid":173121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:21:17.000Z","msg":"老母板Driver ？"},{"pid":"20a9829ec655cd6ae7b4a5b8106cad9658272f50","tid":2510891,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"bios setting?"},{"pid":"9e7561038aa39fd3ece56e1fb99446a735a8d08e","tid":2510891,"uid":354594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"你有無updata 老母？<br />\nlan線都要updata埋"},{"pid":"dd2174fd557fad364ddc40438f4ebef113572eba","tid":2510891,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e7561038aa39fd3ece56e1fb99446a735a8d08e","tid":2510891,"uid":354594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"你有無updata 老母？<br />\nlan線都要updata埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"*update"},{"pid":"88978d90d7268943e7fac1c17e3eced3b771f44c","tid":2510891,"uid":385973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"我都試過<br />\n解決方法如下<br />\n1.先保證Router Firmware同老母板網絡Driver係最Update<br />\n2.檢查所有LAN Port接口(包括老母板LAN Port，Router LAN Port)<br />\n3.直接打俾ISP問<br />\n4.換主板<br />\n5.換Router<br />\n6.你屋苑網絡環境差，直接搬走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b4f3c6c3047d0879c5e07bbc8b916bacde016f","tid":2510891,"uid":79510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"睇下個接線盒 係咪駁咗4條線,要8條先有1000mb<br />\n可能係師傅將4條比電話,4條比電腦/分比兩間房各1部電腦咁駁,定係偷懶唔駁晒8條<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbe7eede89bb10b1fd53f41332bcbdb0cf8c43f","tid":2510891,"uid":68115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:15:25.000Z","msg":"1000mb= 100MB<br />\n完"},{"pid":"c194f553f4e5169af5eaf03c1b331461cb6c9757","tid":2510891,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"頻寬指的是寬頻的速率，其單位是bps（bits per second），即位元速率、位元/秒，寬頻用的單位一般是Mbps，注意這裏的b是小寫的。而電腦中計算儲存容量用的單位是Byte（位元組），更大的存儲容量為MB、GB、TB，注意這裏的B是大寫的，其換算單位是1Byte＝8bit。<br />\n<br />\n也就是說，1MB/s=8Mbps，我們在購買頻寬時的單位和實際使用雖然只是大小寫之分，但其數量卻差了8倍之多。所以100M寬頻（光纖）指的是100Mbps的速率，考慮到少部分的損耗，其下載速度約為12MB/s。"},{"pid":"ae45363ee3047dc3575c2e38e700ebf60fb6b228","tid":2510891,"uid":49015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4b4f3c6c3047d0879c5e07bbc8b916bacde016f","tid":2510891,"uid":79510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"睇下個接線盒 係咪駁咗4條線,要8條先有1000mb<br />\n可能係師傅將4條比電話,4條比電腦/分比兩間房各1部電腦咁駁,定係偷懶唔駁晒8條<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係掛 好似得一條"},{"pid":"87